---
// Compliance and Permits Section - Enhanced from Dry Main
---

<section class="py-16 bg-slate-50">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 uppercase">
          Full Compliance & Permit Management
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Licensed and WSIB-cleared teams installing to Ontario's 2024 Building Code. 
          We handle all permits, inspections, and City of Toronto subsidy applications.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Compliance Grid -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 border-2 border-slate-200">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-cyan-50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 uppercase">Building Code</h3>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-cyan-600 mr-2">✓</span>
              Ontario Building Code 2024 compliant
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-cyan-600 mr-2">✓</span>
              Toronto municipal requirements
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-cyan-600 mr-2">✓</span>
              OHSA & IHSA safety guidelines
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 border-2 border-slate-200">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-cyan-50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 uppercase">Permit Handling</h3>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-cyan-600 mr-2">✓</span>
              Stand-alone drain permits
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-cyan-600 mr-2">✓</span>
              ~10 business days processing
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-cyan-600 mr-2">✓</span>
              Inspection scheduling handled
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 border-2 border-slate-200">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-amber-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 uppercase">Inspection Timeline</h3>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-amber-500 mr-2">✓</span>
              Within ~2 business days
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-amber-500 mr-2">✓</span>
              Final inspection for closure
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-amber-500 mr-2">✓</span>
              All documentation provided
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Specific Requirements Section -->
      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-slate-200 p-8 mb-12">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 uppercase">
          Specific Code Requirements We Follow
        </h3>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-cyan-600 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              Backwater Valve Requirements
            </h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600 ml-7">
              <li>• Full-port (normally open) valves only</li>
              <li>• Stand-alone drain permit required</li>
              <li>• City of Toronto approved models</li>
              <li>• Professional installation certification</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-cyan-600 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              Sump Pump Discharge (By-law 681)
            </h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600 ml-7">
              <li>• Minimum 2m from foundation</li>
              <li>• To permeable surface only</li>
              <li>• Cannot discharge to sanitary sewer</li>
              <li>• Proper grading requirements</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-500 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              Exterior Excavation
            </h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600 ml-7">
              <li>• Ontario One Call locates (5 business days)</li>
              <li>• OHSA trench safety requirements</li>
              <li>• Proper shoring for deep excavations</li>
              <li>• Restoration to original grade</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              Safety Compliance
            </h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600 ml-7">
              <li>• WSIB clearance certificates</li>
              <li>• IHSA safety protocols</li>
              <li>• $5 million liability insurance</li>
              <li>• Licensed master plumbers</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- City Subsidy Information -->
      <div class="bg-cyan-50 border-2 border-green-300 p-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 uppercase">
          City of Toronto Basement Flooding Protection Subsidy
        </h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">
          We handle all subsidy paperwork and ensure you receive maximum rebates up to $3,400
        </p>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Backwater Valve</h4>
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-cyan-600">Up to $1,250</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">80% of costs covered</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Sump Pump</h4>
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-cyan-600">Up to $1,750</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Including installation</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Drain Severance</h4>
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-cyan-600">Up to $400</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Foundation drain disconnect</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-cyan-50 rounded">
          <p class="text-sm text-cyan-700">
            <strong>Note:</strong> Maximum combined subsidy is $3,400. We prepare all permits, schedule inspections, 
            and submit your documentation to ensure approval.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>